title: Best Side Dishes Ever - 1st Edition (2015).epub Gooner
description:
Best Side Dishes Ever - Foolproof Recipes for Greens, Potatoes, Beans, Rice and More - 1st Edition (2015).epub Gooner

Happy Torrents Day 30th March 2016!

Publisher: Countryman Press; 1 edition (September 21, 2015)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1581573227
ISBN-13: 978-1581573220

From tried and true classics to new and exciting flavor profiles, use these exciting sides to spice up any meal

Who wants to eat meat without potatoes? Chicken without rice? Chili without cornbread? Sides can really make the meal. (Sometimes even taking center stage, as Aunt Annie's sweet potato casserole tends to do at the holidays.) Add the perfect compliment to all of your favorite dishes with the delicious--and deliciously healthy--recipes in this book. With many gluten-free and sugar-free options, there's sure to be something for everyone. 70 color photographs
